13
00:00:38,364 --> 00:00:43,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you think you're lucky just to be alive
go for the highest stake in the gamble.</b></font>

14
00:00:43,574 --> 00:00:45,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Same mission creates similar lives.</b></font>

15
00:00:45,794 --> 00:00:48,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But your passion for your dream will make a difference.</b></font>

16
00:00:48,494 --> 00:00:50,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can never use the escalator.</b></font>

17
00:00:50,914 --> 00:00:53,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But you can build up your strength, yeah yeah.</b></font>

18
00:00:53,304 --> 00:00:55,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You must eventually climb the stairs.</b></font>

19
00:00:55,214 --> 00:00:58,094
